data.description: AFFORDABLE Lakefront living with 72’ of water front on the non-motorized Little Timberlake. YOUR OWN DECK for your enjoyment to kayak, etc!  Incredible investment opportunity to own on the lake. Relax and enjoy Lakefront living and also the huge lot size for recreation, gardening, watching the wildlife, Fish off the deck or jump in the lake to swim!! Perfect for paddle boarding, kayaking and more! The Community offers a motorized lake as well, with boat launches, parks, playgrounds, and saltwater access.
